<%- include('./layouts/header') %>
<header>
<div class="section__container header__container">
  <div class="header__content">
    <h1>We Provide Complete Healthcare Service</h1>
    <p>
      Welcome, where exceptional patient experiences are our priority.
      With compassionate care, state-of-the-art facilities, and a
      patient-centered approach, we're dedicated to your well-being. Trust
      us with your health and experience the difference.
    </p>
    <button class="btn">See Services</button>
  </div>
</div>
</header>

<section class="section__container service__container">
<div class="service__header">
  <div class="service__header__content">
    <h2 class="section__header">Our Special service</h2>
    <p>
      Beyond simply providing medical care, our commitment lies in
      delivering unparalleled service tailored to your unique needs.
    </p>
  </div>
  
</div>
<div class="service__grid">
  <div class="service__card">
    <span><i class="fa-solid fa-video"></i></span>
    <h4>Real-time Video Consultations</h4>
    <p>
      Connect with healthcare professionals through our secure and user-friendly video interface. 
    </p>
    
  </div>
  <div class="service__card">
    <span><i class="fa-solid fa-calendar-days"></i></span>
    <h4>Appointment and Schedule Management</h4>
    <p>
      Conveniently schedule appointments online based on healthcare provider's availability
    </p>
  </div>
  <div class="service__card">
    <span><i class="fa-solid fa-laptop-medical"></i></span>
    <h4>Electronic Health Records</h4>
    <p>
      Store, organize, and manage patient's medical information electronically and securely
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
</section>
<section class="section__container about__container">
<div class="about__content">
  <h2 class="section__header">About Us</h2>
  <p>
    Welcome to our teleconsultation platform, your trusted source for accessible and comprehensive healthcare services. We're dedicated to enhancing your well-being through virtual consultations and empowering you with valuable health insights.
  </p>
  <p>
    Explore our diverse range of expertly curated articles and resources, tailored to address your specific health needs. Whether you're seeking guidance on managing medical conditions remotely or tips for optimizing your telehealth experience, our platform is designed to inform, engage, and support you throughout your healthcare journey.
  </p>
  <p>
    Discover practical telemedicine tips and lifestyle recommendations to boost your physical and mental health from the comfort of your home. We believe that leveraging technology for healthcare can lead to meaningful improvements in your overall quality of life, and we're committed to facilitating your journey towards better health and wellness.
  </p>
</div>
<div class="about__image">
  <img src="assets/about.jpg" alt="about" />
</div>
</section>



<footer class="footer">
<div class="section__container footer__container">
  <div class="footer__col">
    <h3>Health<span>Care</span></h3>
    <p>
      We are honored to be a part of your healthcare journey and committed
      to delivering compassionate, personalized, and top-notch care every
      step of the way.
    </p>
    <p>
      Trust us with your health, and let us work together to achieve the
      best possible outcomes for you and your loved ones.
    </p>
  </div>
  <div class="footer__col">
    <h4>About Us</h4>
    <p>Home</p>
    <p>About Us</p>
    <p>Work With Us</p>
    <p>Our Blog</p>
    <p>Terms & Conditions</p>
  </div>
  <div class="footer__col">
    <h4>Services</h4>
    <p>Search Terms</p>
    <p>Advance Search</p>
    <p>Privacy Policy</p>
    <p>Suppliers</p>
    <p>Our Stores</p>
  </div>
  <div class="footer__col">
    <h4>Contact Us</h4>
    <p>
      <i class="fa-solid fa-location-dot"></i> 123, London Bridge Street, London
    </p>
    <p><i class="fa-regular fa-envelope"></i> support@care.com</p>
    <p><i class="fa-solid fa-phone"></i> (+012) 3456 789</p>
  </div>
</div>



